{"tid":2124032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌︰政府應禁海員獲本港檢測報告前在社區活動","createTime":"2020-07-25T05:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T06:00:17.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d75bdb85081d6d3c01aa761521addeed3ef185","tid":2124032,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"許樹昌︰政府應禁海員獲本港檢測報告前在社區活動<br />\n2020-07-25 HKT 12:07<br />\n<br />\n&quot;政府專家顧問、中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌表示，應該不准許海員在港獲得檢測報告前在社區活動......政府可以考慮取消海員在港換班的安排，為期3星期，亦可以參考新加坡的做法，要求海員抵埗後48小時內要離開。 &quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539813-20200725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539813-20200725.htm&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=6e1f238a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539813-20200725.htm&h=aecc04dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539813-20200725.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dbe24bed82491897ef03d871974d5e77706adf72","tid":2124032,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/886aYWo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F886aYWo.png&h=dd613130&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}